ScrollList_Selection event flags
#include Style
#Background wimp 1
#Parent scrolllist_selection
Defined in:	<scrolllist.h=>scrolllist_gadget>
#Line
#Wrap off
Bits:	0 	- Item(s) were selected (otherwise deselected).
	1 	- Indicates mouse double-click by user.
	2 	- Indicates mouse ADJUST-click by user.	(TextGadgets 0.11)
	3 	- Event data includes column number and click coordinates.	(TextGadgets 0.78)
Constants:
	<ScrollList_Selection_Flags_Set>
	<ScrollList_Selection_Flags_DoubleClick>
	<ScrollList_Selection_Flags_AdjustClick>
	<ScrollList_Selection_Flags_ClickData>
#Line
#Wrap on
Flags returned in <ScrollList_Selection> event data.